    <title>Hexo博客问题</title>
    <url>/2020/03/20/hexo/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="hexo图片加载"><a href="#hexo图片加载" class="headerlink" title="hexo图片加载"></a>hexo图片加载</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">相对路径引用：</span><br><span class="line">hexo 中图片加载:</span><br><span class="line">打开_config.yml</span><br><span class="line">post_asset_folder: false（改成true）</span><br><span class="line">建一个和md文件相同的文件夹来存放图片</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% asset_img example.jpg This is an example image %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">绝对路径引用：</span><br><span class="line">当Hexo项目中只用到少量图片时，可以将图片统一放在\themes\next\source\images文件夹中，通过markdown语法访问它们。</span><br><span class="line">![](&#x2F;images&#x2F;image.jpg)</span><br><span class="line">在线引用：</span><br><span class="line">用新郎图床即可</span><br><span class="line">![cat.png](http:&#x2F;&#x2F;ww1.sinaimg.cn&#x2F;large&#x2F;005LmDpBly1gd0qxm26mwj305k05k3yu.jpg)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="首页不显示全文"><a href="#首页不显示全文" class="headerlink" title="首页不显示全文"></a>首页不显示全文</h2><p>官方回答：Use <!-- more --> in your article to break your article manually, which is recommended by Hexo.（在文章中用<!--more-->来分割）<br><img src="http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/005LmDpBly1gd0qxm26mwj305k05k3yu.jpg" alt="cat.png"></p>
]]></content>
